quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  8,49,"Pamene anthu a chinyengo pamodzi ndi anthu amene m’mitima mwawo mudali matenda adati: “Anthu awa ali kunyengedwa ndi chipembedzo chawo.” Koma aliyense amene aika chikhulupiriro chake mwa Mulungu, ndithudi, Mulungu ndi Wamphamvu ndi Wanzeru"
  8,50,"Iwe ukadawaona angelo pamene amachotsa mizimu ya anthu osakhulupirira! Iwo amamenya pa nkhope ndi pa misana yawo nati: “Lawani ululu wa moto wa ku Gahena.”"
  8,51,"“Ichi ndi chifukwa cha zimene manja anu adatsogoza. Ndipo ndithudi, Mulungu sapondereza akapolo ake.”"
  8,52,"Monga anthu a Farao ndi iwo amene adalipo kale, iwo adakana zizindikiro za Mulungu, ndipo Mulungu adawalanga chifukwa cha kulakwa kwawo. Ndithudi Mulungu ndi wamphamvu ndipo amakhwimitsa chilango"
  8,53,"Ichi ndi chifukwa chakuti Mulungu sasintha madalitso amene amapereka kwa anthu mpaka pamene iwo asintha makhalidwe awo, ndipo ndithudi, Mulungu ndi wakumva ndi wodziwa"
  8,54,"Monga anthu a Farawo ndi iwo amene adalipo kale, iwo sadakhulupirire uthenga wa Ambuye wawo kotero Ife tidawaononga chifukwa cha zolakwa zawo ndipo Ife tidamiza anthu a Farawo chifukwa onse adali osalungama"
  8,55,Ndithudi zolengedwa za moyo zimene ndi zoipitsitsa pamaso pa Mulungu ndi anthu osakhulupirira ndipo iwo sadzakhulupirira
  8,56,Iwo ndiwo amene iwe umapanga nawo mapangano koma iwo amaphwanya mapangano awo nthawi zonse ndipo iwo saopa Mulungu
  8,57,"Ngati iwe uwapambana pomenyana nawo nkhondo, alange kwambiri kuti ukhoza kuthamangitsa iwo amene ali kumbuyo kwawo kuti akhoza kuphunzira"
  8,58,"Ngati iwe uopa chinyengo chochokera kwa anthu, nawenso abwezere mwawubwino machitidwe omwewo. Ndithudi Mulungu sakonda anthu aupandu"